## Next Steps
*   **Reverse Flow Draft:** Authors will address feedback on client state management, replay considerations, and determine whether to remove references to the expired consistency draft.
*   **MoLE Proponents:** David Schinazi, Martin Thompson, and other proponents will regroup to draft a charter and consult with the ADs on whether to recharter PRIVACYPASS or pursue a new working group.